Description: Healthcare Market Resources, Inc. provides in-depth, local-market data for hospice and home healthcare marketing. The provided market

Full Description: Healthcare Market Resources, Inc. provides in-depth, local-market data for hospice and home healthcare marketing.  The provided market research is ideal for shaping strategy and tactics for market share, segmentation and business development, as well as for benchmarking financial and operating performance against local competition. Healthcare Market Resources offers two core sets of reports, providing operational, marketing, financial and business development data. These include: - Home Health Care Market Research Reports - Hospice Market Research Reports Healthcare Market Resources was founded by Rick Chesney to fill a need in the home health and hospice industries: the need to base market-related decisions on reliable data, rather than perceptions. Rick Chesney first became involved in home care over 20 years ago and was struck by the dearth of informational resources about the market. Full Description: Hiringcue.com is an automated solution to streamline the reference checking process. Our solution aims to bring about an automated experience to the tedious, time-consuming task of checking references. It takes less than 60 seconds to check references with Hiringcue versus the hours on the phone trying to make contact with referees. After the reference check is complete, users receive a reference report that pinpoints all essential information. Our platform creates a less time consuming and cost-effective experience for companies.  We also offer:  Pre-Interview Questionnaires: You can send a Pre-Interview Questionnaire to candidates before interviewing them. You can choose from our library of over 300 questionnaires or make your own.  Passive Candidate Database: is a byproduct of conducting the reference check. We collect all the referee data, name, email, phone, title, company, area of expertise, etc. when they are giving a reference. Your database will grow over time. Typically, 3-5 references are added for each Reference Check. After 100 reference checks, you will have 300-500 potential candidates/leads in your database. Interview Debrief: “Coming Soon” The interview debrief is a short questionnaire designed to gather all the interviewer’s opinions of the candidate, rate the candidate and make recommendations. Full Description: ShortSwitch is a URL shortening service that allows a customer to use their own domain or sub-domain for shortened URLs. The service provides:  * Branded Short URLs - The service allows you to have your own short URL service using your own domain, without the need to create it yourself. * Smaller Tokens - The short URL tokens start with a single character, and a user will have to create over 195,000 short URLs before the tokens grow past three characters. * Vanity Tokens - The short URL tokens can be customized without worry about their already being in use. The customer can use any token. * Secure Link Creation - Only authorized and authenticated users on the customers account can create short URLs. * API Support - The API supports link creation via various tools. Multiple Users Per Account - The service supports having multiple users on each account. * Reporting - The dashboard provides reporting and statistics on short URLs including the ability to sort and filter by various attributes such as popularity (i.e., most hits) and users. * Google Analytics Integration - The service provides built-in support for easy integration with Google Analytics.
